vegn mayn mamen, mayn mame iz gevezn zeyer religyez,

00:04:43.540 --> 00:04:46.486
ober zi hot nisht azoy fil praktitsirt.

00:04:46.810 --> 00:04:51.135
 zi hot gebetn dem tatn az zol davenen, hot der tate gedavnt.

00:04:51.594 --> 00:04:53.972
er hot gedavnt fraytik tsu nakhts

00:04:54.486 --> 00:04:57.999
in shtub, un shabes in der fri iz er gegangen

00:04:58.243 --> 00:05:02.513
in a spetsyeln plats, aza shtibl, mit zayne fraynt,

00:05:02.648 --> 00:05:07.189
gedavnt. fraytik tsu nakhts, vos ikh gedenk fun di kindere yorn,

00:05:07.621 --> 00:05:09.567
hot er mikh gehaltn bay di hant,

00:05:09.729 --> 00:05:12.405
un gedreyt zikh arum un arum in voynung,

00:05:13.188 --> 00:05:14.999
un er hot hoykh geredt.

00:05:15.161 --> 00:05:18.107
azoy az ikh hob oyfgepast ale verter.

00:05:18.296 --> 00:05:21.756
un kh'hob gedavnt mit im tsuzamen, kh'hob geredt mit im tsuzamen.

00:05:22.918 --> 00:05:26.756
.. vos nokh ken ikh zogn vegn mayne eltern?

00:05:27.134 --> 00:05:32.810
zey zenen, gekumen keyn Yisroel, in nayn in fertsikstn yor,

00:05:33.269 --> 00:05:38.837
un dortn zenen zey bagrobn, eyner lebn andern mit natureln toyt.

00:05:39.215 --> 00:05:47.729
ober zey hobn ibergelebt ven di daytshn zenen ongefaln oyf Poyln.

00:05:48.242 --> 00:05:53.810
un undzer hoyz vu mir hobn gevoynt iz gevorn farbrent in draytsntn

00:05:54.053 --> 00:05:57.688
september. s'iz geven erev ROSH HASHANA.

00:05:57.710 --> 00:05:58.821
NINETEEN THIRTY NINE...

00:05:59.021 --> 00:06:00.621
NINETEEN THIRTY NINE.

00:06:00.972 --> 00:06:05.378
mayn mame iz gegangen tsum beker bakn khales.

00:06:05.432 --> 00:06:09.729
s'iz geven, s'iz geven ariber di di gas.

00:06:09.999 --> 00:06:14.216
un, zi hot shoyn nisht gekent tsurik kumen vayl dos hoyz iz farbrent gevorn.

00:06:14.567 --> 00:06:17.513
m'hot zikh gezukht in di ershte,

00:06:17.945 --> 00:06:25.080
di ershte, bombardirung iz gevezn in draytsntn

00:06:25.270 --> 00:06:28.621
oyf di teyl Varshe vu mir hobn gevoynt. dos heyst

00:06:28.837 --> 00:06:31.080
shpeter iz es gevorn di geto.

00:06:32.513 --> 00:06:37.351
ober ikh hob shoyn nisht gekent dort tsurik kumen. dos hoyz iz farbrent gevorn.

00:06:37.783 --> 00:06:43.486
un oyb ikh darf entfern vi ⟨arumet⟩ s'iz geven di panik,

00:06:43.783 --> 00:06:46.945
mayn tate hot gemakht tsvey pek,

00:06:47.134 --> 00:06:52.080
eyn pak fun di malbushim, fun di shank aroysgenumen,

00:06:52.296 --> 00:06:58.161
un ayngeviklt in a koldre vos iz gelegn di bet- di betn tsugebet.

00:06:59.026 --> 00:07:02.783
er hot aropgevorfn fun dritn shtok, mir hobn gevoynt oyfn dritn shtok.

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:04.972
dernokh hot er gemakht a pak,

00:07:05.431 --> 00:07:08.377
fun, di ontuekhts.

00:07:09.701 --> 00:07:13.999
un, un di tsveyte pak iz gevezn fun,

00:07:14.485 --> 00:07:18.323
fun oykhet mit a koldre un er hot es ayngepakt

00:07:19.566 --> 00:07:23.566
dos dos ontuekhts, er hot es aropgevorfn durkh di zelbn fentster.

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:25.837
un er hot gevolt aropgeyn,

00:07:25.972 --> 00:07:27.837
hobn di shtign gebrent,

00:07:28.242 --> 00:07:31.540
s'iz gevezn hol- hiltserne shtiln, shtign,

00:07:31.837 --> 00:07:35.864
di shtign hobn gebrent, er hot zikh aropgelozt azoy vi yingelekh

00:07:35.999 --> 00:07:37.999
hobn zikh aropgelozt mit eyn fus.

00:07:38.188 --> 00:07:42.513
er iz ge- ven mir hobn im getrofn dray teg shpeter, m'hot im farloyrn,

00:07:42.756 --> 00:07:48.945
m'hot zikh farloyrn in di, in dem, onfang fun, fun di

00:07:49.053 --> 00:07:53.405
 bald in onfang zenen zey gekumen in, oyf undzer gegnt.

00:07:53.621 --> 00:07:58.513
dos heyst dos di yidishe gegnt, dos iz geven an atak oyf di yidishn gegnt.

00:07:59.486 --> 00:08:02.513
iz m'hot zikh farloyrn oyf dray teg mit mayn tatn.

00:08:02.648 --> 00:08:06.188
ven m'hot im gefunen iz er geven bandazhirt. er iz gevezn,

00:08:06.756 --> 00:08:10.918
er iz gevezn opgebrit, opgebrent.

00:08:11.242 --> 00:08:13.674
un m'hot gekrign di ershte hilf.

00:08:14.026 --> 00:08:20.404
un ven er iz aropgekumen hintn, oyf dem hoyf, iz eyn pak gevezn

00:08:20.701 --> 00:08:23.053
tsugenumen fun vemenem, me veyst nisht,

00:08:23.161 --> 00:08:27.296
un der bet-gevant pak hot er gegat, vos hot dernokh gedint

00:08:27.539 --> 00:08:29.701
mayn mame un mayn shvester,

00:08:29.810 --> 00:08:33.377
zenen gevezn tsvey vokhn oyfn gorn himl.

00:08:33.647 --> 00:08:36.080
un untern gorn himl un,

00:08:36.107 --> 00:08:39.350
zenen, di shney iz gefaln, zey zenen gelegn in

00:08:39.458 --> 00:08:44.648
poshetn vaser teyl mol, un in shney un in ho- un in ayz.

00:08:44.891 --> 00:08:49.945
iz damolst iz tsuni- zeyer tsu nits gekumen di koldres untertsuleygn.

00:08:50.107 --> 00:08:52.188
vos mayn tate hot opgeratevet.

00:08:52.648 --> 00:08:55.648
oder ir vilt nor hern vegn mayne eltern?

00:08:55.918 --> 00:09:03.432
un dos iz, der, di zakhn vos ikh gedenk, hob ikh gegat a shvester,

00:09:03.222 --> 00:09:03.950
SARAH...

00:09:04.185 --> 00:09:06.918
SARAH, vos lebt yetst in Yisroel.

00:09:07.405 --> 00:09:11.432
yo zi iz ABOUT zeks yor yunger fun mir.

00:09:11.972 --> 00:09:16.189
un, zi iz geven, mit mir un mit di mame.

00:09:16.378 --> 00:09:20.729
