00:09:20.972 --> 00:09:22.837
umedum hot gebrent.

00:09:22.999 --> 00:09:29.297
Varshe, di teyl, di yidishe teyl fun Varshe, hot a sakh gelitn dem tog.

00:09:29.891 --> 00:09:31.189
m'hot zikh farloyrn.

00:09:31.512 --> 00:09:39.161
m'iz nisht gevezn tsugegreyt oyf azane barbarishe oyfn oyf, oyf an onfal.

00:09:39.458 --> 00:09:43.594
m'hot gevust vos in di politik hot men gehert vos es tut zikh.

00:09:43.702 --> 00:09:45.945
az s'iz noent, efsher dos.

00:09:46.215 --> 00:09:49.594
ober m'hot zikh nisht gekent forshteln az, az s'ken forkumen.

00:09:50.756 --> 00:09:54.810
nokh mir hobn mayne eltern gegat a zun,

00:09:55.539 --> 00:10:01.323
vos, er iz avek fun di velt oyf a, mit a tsufal.

00:10:01.729 --> 00:10:05.891
gevezn gezunt, ⟨ale⟩ kinder zenen geven gezunte kinder.

00:10:06.242 --> 00:10:08.783
BUT mayn mame hot gearbet.

00:10:08.837 --> 00:10:10.458
un zi iz geven a shnayderin.

00:10:10.999 --> 00:10:16.647
un zi iz avekgegangen fun der heym in der fri un s'iz gekumen a mentsh vos hot

00:10:17.026 --> 00:10:20.945
ah badint di kinder un tsugegreyt esn far zey.

00:10:23.593 --> 00:10:32.512
iz a shkheyne hot dertseylt az zi hot gezen durkhn fentster vi di froy, a kristlekhe froy,

00:10:32.593 --> 00:10:35.647
hot aropgelozt dos kind oyf sh- di shteyner.

00:10:36.134 --> 00:10:39.836
der gantse hoyf iz geven gedekt mit shteyner.

00:10:40.026 --> 00:10:43.350
azoy vi kep, kaylekhdike shteyner.

00:10:43.350 --> 00:10:47.377
dos kind iz arop. ven mayn mame iz gekumen bay nakht,

00:10:48.026 --> 00:10:52.377
hot zi gezogt tsu mayn mame az zi muz haynt avekforn tsu zikh in shtub arayn

00:10:52.593 --> 00:10:57.269
in dem derfl fun van zi kumt vayl s'iz dort ver krank, un zi darf helfn.

00:10:57.756 --> 00:11:00.377
mayn mame hot nisht gevust far vos.

00:11:00.972 --> 00:11:03.431
m'hot ir batsolt un zi iz avek.

00:11:03.729 --> 00:11:07.269
tsu morgns hot dos kind gekrign hoykhe temperatur.

00:11:07.837 --> 00:11:14.485
ikh, ikh vil zogn az ikh hob ah v- bashraybungen fun mayn tatn.

00:11:14.566 --> 00:11:17.999
er hot geshribn zayne, zayne,

00:11:18.107 --> 00:11:22.783
tog-teglekhe iberlebenishn fun fun di tsayt.

00:11:23.297 --> 00:11:30.432
