00:11:30.783 --> 00:11:34.134
ikh bin geven fir yor alt un er iz geven tsvey yor alt.

00:11:34.756 --> 00:11:37.864
alzo, nokh tsvey teg iz dos kind avek.

00:11:38.297 --> 00:11:43.729
un m'hot nisht gevust, s'iz gevezn a krankeyt oyfn kop, un m'hot nisht gevust di sibe.

00:11:43.918 --> 00:11:46.432
iz gekumen di shkheyne un zi hot ertseylt.

00:11:46.837 --> 00:11:49.837
dos bashraybt mayn tate vayl ikh hob nisht gekent gedenken.

00:11:49.972 --> 00:11:53.567
ikh gedenk kleyne tsufaln mit dem kind.

00:11:53.702 --> 00:12:00.999
