00:12:01.135 --> 00:12:02.513
un m'hot zikh geshpilt.

00:12:03.026 --> 00:12:05.216
dos iz mir geblibn in gedank.

00:12:05.405 --> 00:12:09.351
vegn mayn shvester iz mer, zenen mir gevaksn tsuzamen un

00:12:09.756 --> 00:12:15.675
