un azoy iz geshen. er hot undz tsugegreyt.

00:15:38.378 --> 00:15:45.107
s'iz nisht gevezn zeyer a sakh, ober s'iz gevezn a, a, a por vokhn.

00:15:45.242 --> 00:15:49.594
un ikh gedenk zayn nomen, er hot geheysn YEREMYA SHROZEN.

00:15:49.837 --> 00:15:54.405
un er iz gevezn a militer-man dernokh, yo.

00:15:55.053 --> 00:15:59.783
un, mir zenen adurkh dem ekzamen, un dos iz gevezn

00:15:59.810 --> 00:16:01.621
vayt fun mayn heym.

00:16:01.729 --> 00:16:04.283
ikh hob gedorfn geyn a sakh.

00:16:04.514 --> 00:16:05.590
HOW OLD WERE YOU THEN?

00:16:08.405 --> 00:16:12.444
ikh bin gevezn fer- fertsn.

00:16:12.474 --> 00:16:13.209
fertsn.

00:16:13.486 --> 00:16:16.333
fertsn yo-,tsi draytsn, tsi fertsn.

00:16:15.494 --> 00:16:16.256
WELL, OK.

00:16:16.935 --> 00:16:17.821
ikh gedenk nisht.

00:16:19.486 --> 00:16:24.107
un dort i- di gimnazye iz geven bloyz yidishe meydlekh.

00:16:24.864 --> 00:16:27.999
s'iz gevezn a, a private shule

00:16:28.107 --> 00:16:31.216
un mir hobn gekrign fuftsik protsent hanokhe.

00:16:33.593 --> 00:16:39.161
kedey me zol zikh kenen, di ershte tsvey yor hot mayn tate far mir getsolt,

00:16:39.161 --> 00:16:41.269
dernokh iz gevorn zeyer shver,

00:16:41.485 --> 00:16:44.350
hob ikh gegebn lektsyes, korepetitsyes.

00:16:44.593 --> 00:16:46.675
un azoy arum hot,

00:16:46.675 --> 00:16:49.648
hob ikh dergreykht tsu endikn di shule.

00:16:50.053 --> 00:16:53.918
vi ikh hob farendikt di shule hob ikh mir fartrakht in vos a veg tsu geyn,

00:16:54.134 --> 00:16:56.648
vayl kh'hob gegat groyse neygungen

00:16:56.648 --> 00:17:00.566
tsu tseykhenen, tsu moln,

00:17:01.756 --> 00:17:07.756
un ikh hob gevolt geyn tsuzamenshteln molerayen mit arkhitektur.

00:17:09.081 --> 00:17:12.135
ober di milkhome iz oysgebrokhn in ershtn september.

00:17:12.351 --> 00:17:16.945
dos iz der tog ven men hot gedorfn onheybn tsu lernen.

00:17:17.270 --> 00:17:23.243
un dos iz geven di tog vos s'iz gevezn a e- an onheyb fun an ende.

00:17:25.431 --> 00:17:27.350
vos nokh vilt ir visn?

00:17:27.512 --> 00:17:32.136
UH, YOU WENT TO STUDY WITH EH A FELLOW CALLED CHAIM GOLDBERG...

00:17:32.873 --> 00:17:35.015
TELL ME ABOUT THAT

00:17:32.886 --> 00:17:35.404
ah, ven ikh bin gevezn

00:17:35.648 --> 00:17:38.350
 akhtsn yor alt,

00:17:38.891 --> 00:17:44.620
 mayn tate iz geboyrn in dem zelbe sh- zelbn shtetl vos,

00:17:44.810 --> 00:17:47.350
vos mayn man.

00:17:48.350 --> 00:17:55.404
ober ikh hob gevolt forn zumer zen mayne kroyvim, mayn tatns, fun mayn tatns zayt.

00:17:56.215 --> 00:17:59.566
bin ikh geforn, ikh bin ayngeshtanen in a,

00:17:59.566 --> 00:18:02.323
mit mayne a kuzine vos iz gevezn oyf

00:18:02.377 --> 00:18:05.242
HAKHSHARA iz zi ayngeshtanen bay undz.

00:18:05.350 --> 00:18:07.945
azoy zi hot mikh zeyer sheyn oyfgenumen.

00:18:08.161 --> 00:18:12.269
un ikh hob aroys, kh'bin aroys in shtetl moln.

00:18:12.458 --> 00:18:14.918
kh'hob gevolt makhn a LANDSCAPE,

00:18:14.945 --> 00:18:19.891
a PIZAR, a sha-, in- fun- in Kazhimizh.

00:18:19.891 --> 00:18:22.864
Kazhimizh iz gevezn zeyer a molerish shtetl.

00:18:23.134 --> 00:18:26.918
s'iz gevezn zeyer a sakh artistn dort.

00:18:27.188 --> 00:18:32.161
un zenen gekumen yor, yor ayn yor oys, shraybers a sakh iz gevezn.

00:18:33.512 --> 00:18:39.566
un, shteyendik azoy iz tsugekumen eyner, un er hot mir gemakht a korekte.

00:18:39.621 --> 00:18:43.485
kh'hob di korekte ongenumen, un s'iz farendikt gevorn.

00:18:43.566 --> 00:18:46.513
um- un far nakht ven s'iz gevorn tunkl,

00:18:46.513 --> 00:18:50.162
hot men ibergegebn di nayes nokh a radyo.

00:18:50.486 --> 00:18:54.729
di radyo iz gevezn, in di shtot,

00:18:55.054 --> 00:18:57.486
keyner hot nisht gegat nokh in shtub keyn radyo.

00:18:57.702 --> 00:19:00.243
nor mentshn hobn, di, di

00:19:00.243 --> 00:19:06.216
di CITY HALL di, di administratsye hot gemakht di radyo in shtetl.

00:19:06.351 --> 00:19:11.351
azoy vi se kumen on zeyer a sakh mentshn oyf di zumer tsayt,

00:19:11.432 --> 00:19:13.189
az zey zoln hern di nayes.

00:19:13.351 --> 00:19:15.945
herndik di nayes mit mayn kuzine,

00:19:15.945 --> 00:19:19.810
hot zi gezogt ikh vel dikh bakenen mit, etlekhe mentshn.

00:19:20.161 --> 00:19:24.351
nokh di nayes hot zi mir, zi hot mir ongevizn, do shteyt eyner,

00:19:24.351 --> 00:19:28.837
geyt ongetun vayse hoyzn, a vays hemd, un shvartse hor.

00:19:29.296 --> 00:19:32.756
un dos dos ershte hot zi mikh bakent mit im.

00:19:33.242 --> 00:19:37.134
kh'hob mikh shoyn nisht badorfn bakenen mit mer keynem, dos iz geven vos...

00:19:37.432 --> 00:19:40.026
un azoy vi zi hot undz bakent

00:19:40.242 --> 00:19:42.756
iz zi gegangen mit undz shpatsirn,

00:19:43.053 --> 00:19:48.567
ober zi hot mikh gegen a loz iber, kh'hob mikh oysgedreyt iz zi shoyn nisht geven. zi hot undz ibergelozt beyde.

00:19:49.107 --> 00:19:56.053
hobn mir zikh opgeshmuest, morgn hob ikh vider geyn mal- moln di PIZAR, un er vet mir gebn instruktsyes, er vet mir zogn vos,

00:19:56.729 --> 00:20:02.432
vayl in akht un draysikstn yor iz er shoyn gevezn nokh di akademye.

00:20:02.432 --> 00:20:06.405
un, s'hot oysgezen az er geyt

00:20:06.810 --> 00:20:10.783
tsum priziv, shteyn tsum priziv, er iz alt gevezn

00:20:10.783 --> 00:20:17.161
eyn un tsvontsik yor. in Poyln iz, hot men ongehoy- genumen in militer arayn bay eyn un tsvontsik yor.

00:20:20.756 --> 00:20:25.513
un ikh bin aheymgekumen, tsurik keyn Varshe,

00:20:26.189 --> 00:20:30.324
un er iz gekumen, hot undz bazukht.

00:20:30.432 --> 00:20:33.837
un m'iz aroysgeforn oyf a oysflug,

00:20:33.837 --> 00:20:38.432
oyf a, unter di shtot, un s'iz arop a shney.

00:20:39.378 --> 00:20:42.080
un s'iz gevorn kalt, un ikh hob mikh tsugekilt.

00:20:42.350 --> 00:20:44.999
iz er gekumen bazukhn ven ikh bin

00:20:45.080 --> 00:20:50.594
gevezn in a, a bisl kranklekhn tsushtand. s'hot nisht lang gedoyert.

00:20:52.621 --> 00:21:01.756
in, detsember OR yanuar nayn un draysik

00:21:02.431 --> 00:21:04.134
iz er geshtanen tsum priziv.

00:21:04.296 --> 00:21:08.675
er iz geven toyb fun kindvayz on.

00:21:08.810 --> 00:21:15.350
er hot gegat shkarletine un dos zenen gevezn di rezultatn fun di krankeyt.

00:21:15.864 --> 00:21:21.269
 zayn nomen iz gevezn Leyb. nisht Khayim.

00:21:22.080 --> 00:21:27.431
ober in der moment, di eltern hobn gefilt s'iz z- zeyer a ernste minut.

00:21:28.026 --> 00:21:29.648
zenen zey gegangen tsum RABBI.

00:21:29.945 --> 00:21:35.972
hot der RABBI gezogt, "gib im tsu a nomen Khayim vet er blaybn barn lebn."

00:21:35.972 --> 00:21:37.377
un azoy iz geven.

00:21:37.485 --> 00:21:41.512
hot er dernokh hot er dem Leyb avekgeshtelt un er iz geblibn mitn Khayim.

00:21:41.756 --> 00:21:44.026
azoy az es hot zikh geendert.

00:21:45.107 --> 00:21:46.620
vos nokh?

00:21:46.620 --> 00:21:50.674
IN NINETEEN THIRTY NINE WHEN THE GERMANS CAME

00:21:50.836 --> 00:21:53.999
YOU AND CHAIM AND THE FAMILY ESCAPED

00:21:54.188 --> 00:21:56.202
FROM POLAND. WHERE DID YOU GO?

00:21:57.296 --> 00:22:00.512
ikh vil dertseyln vegn zayn militer.

00:22:00.512 --> 00:22:02.639
un dernokh vet men tsukumen tsu dem.

00:22:01.944 --> 00:22:02.350
OK.

00:22:04.107 --> 00:22:08.134
nisht kukndik oyf dem vos er iz geven toyb,

00:22:08.593 --> 00:22:10.741
hot men im in militer arayn ongenumen.

00:22:10.804 --> 00:22:12.123
yo, I KNOW.

00:22:11.398 --> 00:22:14.323
m'hot afile k- nisht gemakht keyn bamiung

00:22:14.594 --> 00:22:16.756
tsu gebn a kuk vos iz mit di oyern.

00:22:16.800 --> 00:22:17.280
yo.

00:22:17.350 --> 00:22:18.269
er hot

00:22:18.269 --> 00:22:23.485
gezogt az "ikh her nisht, ikh bin toyb, di oyern..."

00:22:24.053 --> 00:22:26.783
hobn zey geentfert, "ale yidn hobn azoy.

00:22:27.188 --> 00:22:30.566
oder do oder dort tut zey vey," ikh vil nisht onvayzn.

00:22:31.458 --> 00:22:33.215
m'hot im ongenumen in militer arayn.

00:22:33.539 --> 00:22:36.431
er hot gegat k- a kaker in militer.

00:22:36.729 --> 00:22:38.431
vayl vos m'hot geredt

00:22:38.778 --> 00:22:40.070
hert er nisht

00:22:38.802 --> 00:22:41.945
hot men im geheysn nokhzogn. zey hobn gevust az er hert nisht.

00:22:41.972 --> 00:22:44.080
m'hot im geheysn nokhzogn.

00:22:44.296 --> 00:22:45.404
hot gezogt,

00:22:45.972 --> 00:22:50.107
"JA NIE SLYSZY PANIE UNK GENERAL."

00:22:50.107 --> 00:22:50.701
UNK

00:22:50.999 --> 00:22:53.674
"UNK"

00:22:53.918 --> 00:22:55.242
UNK

00:22:55.242 --> 00:22:58.539
"fal in di blote! un heyb dikh oyf.

00:22:59.296 --> 00:23:02.620
tsen mol. yetst vestu hern?"

00:23:02.620 --> 00:23:03.972
"neyn ikh her nisht."

00:23:03.972 --> 00:23:06.026
"loyf hundert meter,

00:23:06.026 --> 00:23:08.161
mit alem ding oyf di pleytse."

00:23:08.323 --> 00:23:10.593
"fal dort in di blote!"

00:23:10.593 --> 00:23:14.620
zey hobn zikh zeyer nekome genumen in im vayl er iz geven a yid.

00:23:14.729 --> 00:23:17.729
hot er bashlosn tsu endern dos, ikh bin gef-

00:23:17.729 --> 00:23:20.648
tsvey mol geforn im bazukhn in di armey.

00:23:20.756 --> 00:23:27.810
er hot bashlosn tsu endern vi nokh aroystsukrign zikh fun di, fun di situatsye.

00:23:28.135 --> 00:23:38.027
er hot, gemakht a detsizye tsu oyftsumoln epes.

00:23:38.837 --> 00:23:44.540
g- genoy gedenk ikh nisht, tsi portret vemener, tsi epes farn militer,

00:23:44.540 --> 00:23:47.054
er hot gemakht epes an arbet.

00:23:47.243 --> 00:23:49.000
un s'iz zeyer gefoln.

00:23:49.216 --> 00:23:51.810
un m'hot im gezogt, mer vestu nisht geyn of keyn

00:23:51.810 --> 00:23:54.216
shvere zakhn. yetst vestu makhn dos.

00:23:54.216 --> 00:24:00.243
er hot dergreykht zayn, zayn farlang iz gevorn nokhgegebn.

00:24:00.243 --> 00:24:01.270
er hot dergreykht.

00:24:03.000 --> 00:24:07.349
un dernokh iz, in nayn un draysik- dos iz geven nayn un draysikster yor.

00:24:07.513 --> 00:24:08.285
di milkhome...

00:24:07.724 --> 00:24:11.594
ven di milkhome iz aroysgebrokhn iz er geven in militer.

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:16.729
ven der plats vi er hot gedint

00:24:17.243 --> 00:24:22.945
iz gevorn farnumen fun di daytshn, oder zenen geven zeyer noent, hot men zey evakuirt, di zelner.

00:24:22.945 --> 00:24:25.702
m'hot zey geheysn geyn in rikhtung fun Varshe.

00:24:26.107 --> 00:24:30.324
zenen zey ale gegangen in rikhtung fun Varshe. er hot erkent

00:24:30.837 --> 00:24:35.513
a strategishn gefil hot er zeyer shtark antviklt.

00:24:35.513 --> 00:24:38.432
me zogt az ale mener hobn azoy, nu.

00:24:39.026 --> 00:24:43.972
alzo er hot erkent az dos hoyz vu mir hobn gevoynt,

00:24:43.972 --> 00:24:50.242
fun der vaytns hot er erkent, iz geblibn shteyn farbrent.

00:24:50.242 --> 00:24:52.945
s'iz nishto keyn zeykher dort fun keyn mentshn.

00:24:52.945 --> 00:24:58.378
er hot zikh opgebetn me zol im lozn geyn zen dem plats.

00:24:58.486 --> 00:25:00.513
hot men im gelozt.

00:25:00.513 --> 00:25:05.107
er iz tsugekumen hot er gezen alts iz farbrent, keyn mentshn zenen nisht do,

00:25:05.296 --> 00:25:07.945
vu geyt men yetst zukhn?

00:25:08.215 --> 00:25:11.756
er hot gegat shvestern in Varshe,

00:25:12.053 --> 00:25:15.702
iz er gegangen mit di militer

00:25:16.243 --> 00:25:25.891
vu m'hot zey geheysn arayngeyn in a hoyf, un dort zikh makhn bakvem, un makhn dort di kikh,

00:25:25.891 --> 00:25:28.432
un fun dort veln zey shisn az me vet darfn.

00:25:29.918 --> 00:25:33.864
ven mir zenen dertlofn, ikh mit mayn mame, un mayn shvester,

00:25:33.891 --> 00:25:35.351
vos kh'hob frier dertseylt,

00:25:35.729 --> 00:25:39.675
mayn tate iz nisht gevezn mit undz, hersht nokh dray teg hot men im gefunen,

00:25:40.026 --> 00:25:43.783
iz men gelofn azoy vayt vu m'hot gezen a gas vu

00:25:44.108 --> 00:25:45.837
dos fayer iz nisht derganen.

00:25:46.675 --> 00:25:48.918
iz men dort arayngelofn,

00:25:48.918 --> 00:25:55.567
un in keler dort hot men gemakht a plats far di vos zenen dertlofn fun fayer.

00:25:55.567 --> 00:26:00.297
m'hot afile g- tsugegreyt dort tsu esn far di mentshn.

00:26:00.459 --> 00:26:04.810
ikh gedenk az s'iz geven gekokhte rayz, mit floymen.

00:26:13.702 --> 00:26:15.829
JUST KEEP TALKING. FORGET ABOUT THE NOISE.

00:26:15.945 --> 00:26:19.621
di rayz, alzo s'iz gevezn,

00:26:19.621 --> 00:26:22.270
un tsumorgns in der fri

00:26:23.378 --> 00:26:26.864
hot men gezen Khayim kumt undz zen!

00:26:27.134 --> 00:26:32.594
zayn gantse, di grupe, vos iz gekumen keyn Varshe,

00:26:32.675 --> 00:26:35.513
hot men geheysn arayngeyn in dem hoyz, un dos iz geven

00:26:35.513 --> 00:26:36.999
eyn hoyz lebn andern.

00:26:36.999 --> 00:26:38.567
vu mir zenen geshtanen.

00:26:38.567 --> 00:26:40.161
geven a tsufal.

00:26:40.270 --> 00:26:44.864
hot undz gebrengt tsu esn, mir, mayn tatn, mayn mamen, mayn shvester,

00:26:45.297 --> 00:26:47.837
un m'hot zikh gezen yedn tog.

00:26:48.351 --> 00:26:52.837
s'iz gevezn a, aroystsugeyn fun dortn un arayngeyn do iz UNK...

00:26:54.972 --> 00:26:56.972
fun vant hot men zikh dervust?

00:26:56.972 --> 00:26:59.783
er iz gegangen tsu di shvester,

00:27:00.324 --> 00:27:03.621
di shvester hob ikh, hot mikh getrofn oyf di gas,

00:27:03.675 --> 00:27:05.567
hob ikh ir gezogt vu ikh shtey,

00:27:05.702 --> 00:27:09.864
un dernokh hot er zikh getrofn mit di shvester, hot zi im gezogt az mir zenen azoy noent.

00:27:13.080 --> 00:27:18.053
dos iz geven a tsayt ven Varshe, halb Varshe,

00:27:18.269 --> 00:27:24.567
di yidishe gegnt, di yidishe gegnt, iz gevorn bombardirt,

00:27:24.675 --> 00:27:27.242
s'hot shoyn nisht ekzistirt.

00:27:29.945 --> 00:27:32.269
vos vilt ir nokh hern fun mir?

00:27:30.905 --> 00:27:31.313
OK

00:27:32.287 --> 00:27:32.955
WE'LL CONTINUE.
